@startuml
title Arc Agent - Thread Lifecycle Overview

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> NewThread : create thread_id
NewThread --> Running : first message

state Running {
  [*] --> Planning
  Planning --> ToolExecution : tool needed
  ToolExecution --> WaitingApproval : destructive tool (arc_close_tab)
  WaitingApproval --> ToolExecution : user approves
  WaitingApproval --> Planning : user denies/edits
  ToolExecution --> Planning : tool result returned
  Planning --> Finalizing : answer ready
}

Running --> Checkpointing : run completes
Checkpointing --> Idle

Idle --> Running : next user message
Idle --> Archived : user archives thread / cleanup policy

Archived --> Running : reopen archived thread
Archived --> [*] : permanent deletion

Running --> Failed : runtime error
Failed --> Idle : retry later
Failed --> [*] : delete thread
@enduml
